STATE EX REL. LENEGHAN
v.
HUSTED 2018-0866 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 8, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

In Mandamus. Sua sponte, parties ordered to file a response, if any, to relators' motion to expedite and motion for an order pursuant to Civ.R. 65 for temporary injunctive relief no later than 5:00 p.m. on Friday, August 10, 2018.
